	Penelope engaged    
	 New York, Oct. 5 (PTI): Actress Penelope Cruz and her actor beau Javier Bardem have reportedly got engaged and are planning to get married soon.      
	The couple, who remain tight-lipped about the status of their relationship, have been telling their friends about the engagements, reports the New York Daily News. Rumours that they might be engaged have been floating around since April.    
	Drew pies     
	London (PTI): Actress Drew Barrymore, who turned director with Whip It, showed her roller-skating skills on Jimmy Fallons late-night TV show when she tried to break a record for hitting strangers with cream pies. Barrymore was given 30 seconds to hit members of the audience with pies. She managed to hit 14 before tripping and falling on her face.                                                                                                                                                                                   
